reviewText: This presentation was by a Christian organization and not true to the original story line.  Not good for public school with a diverse clientele.  The acting, costumes, very bad and ameturish.
Very poor quilty.......story was not right.
Great I am using this for my English class.
A beautiful, sensitive retelling of O Henry's classic tale of love, grace and redemption. A perfect film for the annual family gathering.
